OL,3,CMeet the man who can't remember his
OL,4,Cown wedding day
OL,6,FBob Sutcliffe's epilepsy means he
OL,7,Fcannot remember his wedding day, as
OL,8,FFiona Marley Paterson reports.
OL,10,FBob Sutcliffe loves to paint. The calm
OL,11,Fand concentration it brings help him
OL,12,Fmanage his epilepsy.
OL,14,FBut when Bob tries to remember a
OL,15,Fspecial event, often he simply cannot
OL,16,Fpicture it in his mind.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/9
