OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1779369077
OL,3,CMeet the man who can't remember his
OL,4,Cown wedding day
OL,6,FFor example, Bob cannot recall any of
OL,7,Fhis wedding day. To reminisce about
OL,8,Fthis or many other special events, he
OL,9,Fhas to rely on his wife to fill in the
OL,10,Fgaps.
OL,12,FBob started to have seizures aged 36,
OL,13,Fand it was then when his memory
OL,14,Ftroubles started.
OL,16,FThe Grange Over Sands resident told
OL,17,FITV Border: "That was that pivotal
OL,18,Fmoment where my memory loss began. We
OL,19,Fwere grieving the loss of what I was
OL,20,Flike."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1779369077
OL,3,CMeet the man who can't remember his
OL,4,Cown wedding day
OL,6,FBob's wife Jan interjected: "It
OL,7,Fchanged our lives. From that moment,
OL,8,Freally."
OL,10,FBob cannot remember his first dance
OL,11,Fwith his wife, or seeing her walk down
OL,12,Fthe aisle. The couple have pictures
OL,13,Ffrom the event, but these fail to jog
OL,14,FBob's memory.
OL,16,FBob said: "It's only our memories that
OL,17,Fare really important.
OL,19,F"But really, they're only Jan's. So it
OL,20,Fis sad."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1779369077
OL,3,CMeet the man who can't remember his
OL,4,Cown wedding day
OL,6,FJan said: "It would be lovely to be
OL,7,Fable to say, 'do you remember when we
OL,8,Fdid this?' And he remembers it.
OL,10,F"So you know, from the photographs,
OL,11,Fit's brilliant that we've got that,
OL,12,Fbut he just can't remember, like the
OL,13,Ffirst dance or what we had for food or
OL,14,Fanything like that."
OL,16,FRebekah Smith, Chief Executive of
OL,17,FEpilepsy Action, said Bob is far from
OL,18,Fbeing alone.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
